Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.24,0:00:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝会时辰到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百官入朝见驾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹孟德昨天跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日天黑之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.35,0:00:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必将董贼的首级悬于宫门呐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个时辰呐 应该得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果一旦有了好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就禀报陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们也要做好应急的准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.36,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们大汉就要云破天开了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.63,0:00:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊 我们早做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听着 日落之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.84,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼首级必将悬于宫门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭迎丞相入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将率军追出百里开外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.66,0:01:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仍见不到曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.56,0:01:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过末将已将军马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安置在各个要道口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.56,0:01:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继续搜捕曹操 谅他也跑不了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.77,0:01:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣等恭迎相国入朝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.96,0:01:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操那个杂种 狗胆包天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟敢行刺咱家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.07,0:01:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家是什么人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家是上天遣下来的丞相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是来中兴大汉王朝的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何人能刺得了咱家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.95,0:01:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些个贼子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:02:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家打眼一瞅就能瞅出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抽鼻子一闻就能闻出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们当中就有曹操的主使
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.16,0:02:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍的内应
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家恨不得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把你们这些狼心狗肺的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都给我揪出来砍了 砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后咱家就把他们这些肉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿来炖汤喝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.25,0:02:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有人说这肉酸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可咱家说了咱家不怕酸 不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.56,0:02:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国言过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.36,0:02:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}皇宫里没有贼子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.97,0:02:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太常卿何在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你即刻用天子的玉玺发布诏令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}火速传到各个郡 州 县
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.55,0:03:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就说曹操大逆不道 弑主悖君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也要着各地军民人等抓捕曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果谁能把曹操的首级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}献上京城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷赏千金 封万户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.07,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣即刻拟旨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王司徒 王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.25,0:03:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相国
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.35,0:03:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前天是你的六十大寿 对不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.55,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足下在府上大排宴席 对不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足下请了那么多的公卿大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.93,0:03:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么不请咱家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:04:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫贱降 寒舍简陋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下不敢惊动相国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}莫非是你那一杯寿酒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家不配喝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.26,0:04:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寒舍的酒 酒 酒酸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}酒酸 咱家说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不怕酸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公下朝了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你立刻把府上的家丁仆妇们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.05,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全都遣散
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}散给他们铜钱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们能上哪儿去就上哪儿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.36,0:04:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别跟我殉葬喽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你也走吧 不用管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吴伯 有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公今天下朝神情不对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怕是有大祸将至啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你赶紧进去 小心侍候着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最好能问个明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 万万使不得 万万使不得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是叫你们马上离开这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你怎么还不走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 到底发生了什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何必如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操行刺董贼失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董贼怀疑我是曹操的背后主使
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.06,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}用不了多久
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.96,0:06:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那群西凉猛夫们就会来到这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要是再不走我就被灭门了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.96,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 你刚才说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓怀疑你是曹操的主使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是这么说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错 是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他并没有确定 对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是不能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为曹操并没有被他们捕获啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.05,0:07:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你就更不能自尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你想啊 如果你自尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不就是等于不打自招
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主动承认你就是曹操的主使了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 你若是死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就是天子无助 朝廷无望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}府宅上下八十几口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要被斩尽杀绝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有啊 你中兴汉室的大愿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不也就永远都不能实现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中郎将吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}带领西凉军士闯进府门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.28,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 你不能犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须去见他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.18,0:08:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是当朝的司徙大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不会把你怎么样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是奉先哪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有何事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀司徒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将奉相国令 来此搜捕曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那曹操奸滑无比
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他谋刺失败了逃命还来不及呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂敢躲在我这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}军士们既然追出百里开外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都没能追捕到曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那他很可能根本就没有出城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.37,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是躲藏于京师贼巢当中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国好见识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫这座府院竟然是个贼巢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.29,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒见谅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将只能奉命而行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.26,0:10:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道知道 将军请自便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我搜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.47,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点 快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们几个去那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仔细点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那边有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.68,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在去那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.98,0:10:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.39,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我搜仔细点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去前院看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是王允大人的义女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知将军有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下吕布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.79,0:11:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}奉董相国令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.69,0:11:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前来搜捕逆贼曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操 我知道这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前天我义父过六十大寿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结果曹操不请自来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}非要给我义父祝寿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想到被我义父给痛骂了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}骂他是奸猾小人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:12:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并派人把他给叉出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真把他给叉出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的 我是亲眼所见的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}府上上下都看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.59,0:12:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军若是不信可以详查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.09,0:12:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是王司徒祖传的七星刀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将军真的是好眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 这就是七星刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.57,0:12:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此看来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王司徒并没有把七星刀送给曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.48,0:13:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父怎么会把七星刀送给曹操呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要送 也要送一位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}配得上这把宝刀的大英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.99,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 既然七星刀在府上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就说明王司徒并非贼党
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}司徒大人与曹操行刺并无牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然是没有牵连的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我义父和董相国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有将军你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.10,0:13:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都是朝廷的大忠臣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢小姐夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}叨扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操并未在此 走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄天后土 日月乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刘备 关羽 张飞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在桃园中结为异姓兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此生此世 同心协力 荣辱与共
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.08,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上报国家 下安黎庶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.88,0:14:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不求同年同月同日生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但愿同年同月同日死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:15:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}耿耿此心 惟天可表 万世不移
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.29,0:15:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这又抓谁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.99,0:15:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这怎么又抓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:16:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来 检查检查 快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走 走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}推车的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把头转过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人就是钦犯 给我拿下 拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的拿住钦犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是何人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小的沛国客商
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}复姓皇甫 名章
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这几位军爷是认错了人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.61,0:17:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把小的拿来了 请大人明察
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操 曹孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你竟如此健忘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两年前我到京师去求官
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还登门拜访过你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当时你架子可是够大的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}连我投拜的名刺看都不看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.67,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就让你手下掷还于我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还顺便送了我一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.40,0:17:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么当今奸臣当道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}京官不做也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是陈公台
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在下有眼不识圣贤 多有得罪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.99,0:18:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过就算是你今天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仍到我府上去求官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.79,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还是那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当今奸臣当道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}京官不做也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我气的倒不是你说的这几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我气得是你连面都不见我一见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.61,0:18:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹阿瞒啊 曹阿瞒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你历来是轻狂傲慢 狂妄自大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}藐视天下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阶下之囚啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不敢与县令大人论天下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也不屑于和你这个钦犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}论什么天下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和你论天下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.80,0:19:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还不如听听我的蛐蛐叫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天我倒是想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟你论一论柴米油盐的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿下你曹操的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赏千金 封万户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听清了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}千金哪 值三十万石谷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.89,0:19:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相当于我一个县令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三百七十五年的官俸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相当于中牟县
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.66,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全县百姓一年的口粮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还要外加上一个万户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.81,0:19:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今往后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我陈宫可是要坐拥金山了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.41,0:19:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是闹不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你连皮带肉也就一百多斤重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.82,0:19:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么会值千金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那悬赏之人是不是瞎了眼睛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 不要再罗嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尽管拿着曹某的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到董贼那儿去领赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我只有一个要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.50,0:20:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给我一把快刀 免得爷爷遭罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错 不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死到临头了还挺有股子英雄之气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别着急
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.62,0:20:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天一早我就会准备一口坛子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}装上你的脑袋 奔赴京师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过今天晚上嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好歹你还是我本官的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人哪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让他尝尝中牟县大牢的厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大牢伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走 走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大人 大人给点吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我快饿死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大人 放了我吧 我没罪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}据我所知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓对你不薄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为何要刺杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.93,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}燕雀安知鸿鹄之志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我这只燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倒还真想知道你的鸿鹄之志
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我历代祖上世食汉禄 世受皇恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:21:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我曹操不思报国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.61,0:21:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与禽兽何异
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.72,0:22:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今奸贼当道 生灵涂炭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.82,0:22:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正臣授首 仕子蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.02,0:22:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}四百年的大汉江山危在旦夕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}越是在这危难当中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就越是英雄辈出之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.80,0:22:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}凡我志士仁人都可杀贼建功
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}振兴汉室 治国平天下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而欲救国就必先诛杀董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正是为了杀贼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才不得不屈身事贼以谋求时机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄真乃无双国士 智勇超群
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.33,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请受陈宫一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这是为何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.11,0:22:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.01,0:23:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大堂之上人多眼杂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.41,0:23:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫我不得不折辱你一番
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是报我当年登门受辱之愤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知道吗 我早就恨透了国贼董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早就想手提三尺剑 手刃国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而恰恰是你做了我想做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而没有办法做到的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.40,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫深表敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我料事不周啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刺杀失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仓惶逃出京师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}亡命于荒郊野地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然刺贼没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:23:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是孟德兄已经名垂青史
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.93,0:23:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不以成败论英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实话说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.43,0:24:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对干刺杀这件事我已经后悔了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.41,0:24:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此话什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.52,0:24:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我曹操何许人也
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.02,0:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我应该振臂高呼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.02,0:24:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}召集天下的壮士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.02,0:24:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}组建剿贼义军
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}挽江山于既倒 救苍生于水火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.33,0:24:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}干一番轰轰烈烈的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这才是我应该做的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.43,0:24:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而这恰恰也是最难做的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.94,0:24:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我挑了一个容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.91,0:24:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}避重就轻拿了一把刀去刺杀董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.11,0:24:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我曹操居然堕入刺客之流了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.32,0:24:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓又是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.32,0:24:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不配我去刺杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.52,0:24:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再者说了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.32,0:24:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是董卓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.32,0:24:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道就没有别的袅雄祸国乱世
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.73,0:25:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 曹操刺董
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看上去是大智大勇
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.53,0:25:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}实则
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.44,0:25:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}匹夫之勇 愚蠢之至
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.11,0:25:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄此话令我如梦方醒
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.41,0:25:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汗颜哪汗颜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.62,0:25:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我正为你此壮举敬佩不已之时
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.12,0:25:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你已经将它视如草芥了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.73,0:25:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这也是拜你所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在这间牢房里
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.50,0:25:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}痛定思痛悟出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.93,0:25:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敢问孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.04,0:25:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此去何为
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.54,0:25:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}归乡里 发天子诏
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.31,0:25:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}召集天下诸侯 兴兵讨伐董卓
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.21,0:25:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}重整山河 再造乾坤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.02,0:25:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫有一愿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.62,0:26:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}务请孟德兄允诺
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.93,0:26:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.23,0:26:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请准许我随你鞍前马后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.03,0:26:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}辅助明公 共创大业
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.64,0:26:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可是朝廷命官啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.11,0:26:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不也是朝廷的一名骁骑校尉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.01,0:26:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀贼易 成大业难
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.22,0:26:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一旦把大旗举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.62,0:26:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等随时都有粉身碎骨的危险
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.12,0:26:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了乾坤大业
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.03,0:26:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫我不避刀山火海
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.93,0:26:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.43,0:26:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我如今是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.24,0:26:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的父母 妻子 孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.64,0:26:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.41,0:27:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}罢了 陈宫已经顾不得许多了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.32,0:27:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只当是陈宫从来就没有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.83,0:27:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.54,0:27:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}国士无双 义薄云天
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.44,0:27:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}曹某敬佩之至
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.91,0:27:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.52,0:27:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陈宫与孟德兄并立于此
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.12,0:27:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是国士成双吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.33,0:27:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受我一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.62,0:28:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位仁兄 陈宫告罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.02,0:28:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要和曹操举义讨贼
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.03,0:28:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共建英雄大业
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.43,0:28:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起了 对不起你们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.74,0:28:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.84,0:29:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由此北去五百余里即是平阳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.15,0:29:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说袁绍已经在平阳起兵了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.32,0:29:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不错 袁本初是个聪明人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.62,0:29:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在这乱世之中抢先举起了义旗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.43,0:29:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为天下先哪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.33,0:29:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁氏家族名动四海 四世三公
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.64,0:29:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可以说是名门故旧遍布天下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.94,0:29:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍举兵 各地诸侯必然云集
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.44,0:29:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看咱们不如先投奔于他
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.95,0:29:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}共襄大义
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.95,0:29:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公台兄
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.82,0:29:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得咱们肯定是要去见袁绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是如果现在单枪匹马的去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.13,0:29:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不会得到重用
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.13,0:30:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.83,0:30:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得袁绍并非明主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.44,0:30:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄 此话何意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.04,0:30:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问 袁绍为何举兵
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.35,0:30:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这还用问哪
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.45,0:30:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讨伐董卓 锄贼扶汉
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.65,0:30:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.22,0:30:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董卓之患又从何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.43,0:30:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.43,0:30:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先帝中平末年
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.93,0:30:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}君臣昏昏 宦党擅权
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.43,0:30:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以张让为首的十常侍把持朝政
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.84,0:30:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当时何进为了剿除宦党
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}密令西凉诸侯率兵入京勤王
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.04,0:30:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这才造成了董卓的祸乱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.85,0:30:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.05,0:30:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}召藩入京勤王这个主意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.85,0:30:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是谁出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.95,0:30:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个我倒不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.26,0:31:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.72,0:31:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.03,0:31:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是他向何进建议
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.13,0:31:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}密令西凉刺史董卓引军入京
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.03,0:31:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}后头的结果就有目共睹了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.14,0:31:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阉宦之祸倒是没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.74,0:31:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是董卓之祸甚干阉宦之祸十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.84,0:31:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来这袁本初真是徒有虚名
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.85,0:31:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没有远见卓识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.55,0:31:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我再问你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.25,0:31:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.95,0:31:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第一个便反对召藩入京勤王
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.06,0:31:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又是谁最早就看出董卓之祸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.13,0:31:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会甚于阉宦之祸的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.43,0:31:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.43,0:31:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我曹某
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.13,0:31:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当日何进和袁绍商议此事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.44,0:31:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就在边儿上
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我跟他们说
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.74,0:31:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阉宦之祸古今皆有
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.24,0:31:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但看天子是否贤明
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.45,0:31:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要有明主在朝
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.75,0:32:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只需以迅雷不及掩耳之势
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}派一小吏便可将阉宦付之牢狱
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.36,0:32:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是召藩入京勤王却万万不可
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.36,0:32:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为那是引虎驱狼之计
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.43,0:32:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其结果断然是虎患大于狼害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.23,0:32:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是何进不听
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.53,0:32:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他认为袁绍四世三公
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.34,0:32:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}肯定比我曹操有见识
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.64,0:32:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}结果呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.14,0:32:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}西凉军来了 何进死了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.44,0:32:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍跑了 董卓祸害后宫
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.15,0:32:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荼毒天下
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.05,0:32:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当初他们要是听了你曹孟德的话
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.76,0:32:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何至于今日啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.36,0:32:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饿殍遍地 虎狼横行
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.23,0:32:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}山河破碎 民不聊生
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.13,0:32:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这就是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.24,0:32:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不听我曹操的话的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.65,0:33:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.06,0:33:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}卖水喽 卖水喽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.86,0:33:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大爷 你喝点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.03,0:33:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不喝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.73,0:33:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的画像已经传到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.24,0:33:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也成了你的从犯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你的头颅值千金
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.74,0:33:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的头颅只值五十金
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.84,0:33:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 我的脑袋太贵
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.74,0:33:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的又太便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.95,0:33:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德兄
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.25,0:33:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中原大旱 颗粒无收
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.55,0:33:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各地的百姓早就有人易子而食了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.75,0:33:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}饥民们为了半斗粮谷
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.86,0:33:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不惜挺而走险 卖友求利
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.86,0:33:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷如此重赏
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.43,0:33:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就等于把我们变成了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.13,0:33:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所有人梦寐以求的猎物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.74,0:34:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说得是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.64,0:34:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你我身负大业
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.84,0:34:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果死于鹰犬之手岂不可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.54,0:34:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们绕过这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.84,0:34:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找个地方歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.14,0:34:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从此后昼伏夜行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.45,0:34:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此地离陇山已经不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.65,0:34:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说那里的百姓
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.05,0:34:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不奉朝廷号令 武装自保
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.55,0:34:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}陇山
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.76,0:34:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那儿是不是有个小县叫成皋县
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.96,0:34:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像是有
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.56,0:34:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们就去那儿歇息
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.06,0:34:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.34,0:34:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吁
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.14,0:34:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尔等何人 竟敢闯到这儿来
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.54,0:34:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请问壮士 吕伯奢在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.45,0:34:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.25,0:34:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就劳烦壮士通禀一声
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.35,0:34:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就说刺董失败的钦犯曹操
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.65,0:34:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.85,0:34:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.45,0:34:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果提曹操的首级献入京城
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.56,0:34:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷赏千金 封万户侯
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.96,0:34:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德呀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.16,0:34:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.46,0:35:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有中牟县令陈公台
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.76,0:35:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和曹操一起前来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.77,0:35:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如提陈公台的首级献入京城
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.84,0:35:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}朝廷赏五十金
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.94,0:35:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀我主 曹操拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.74,0:35:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德呀 你这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.14,0:35:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这的地主吕伯奢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.64,0:35:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我父亲的结义兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.75,0:35:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此人急公好义 绝不会卖友
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.25,0:35:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相反 如果我把底细直接告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.35,0:35:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}倒会引起他的敬重
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.15,0:35:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道你就如此信任这个吕伯奢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.26,0:35:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这么跟你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.46,0:35:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就是信不过我自个儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.26,0:35:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也绝不会信不过吕伯奢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.86,0:35:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快开门 开门去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.67,0:35:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}开门
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.37,0:35:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}侄儿啊 侄儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.14,0:35:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.74,0:35:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}侄儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.74,0:35:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.24,0:35:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是侄儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.14,0:35:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我啊 是我曹阿瞒哪
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.85,0:35:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天有眼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.35,0:35:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.65,0:35:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.95,0:35:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是你啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.05,0:35:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.26,0:36:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从州县到乡里
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.26,0:36:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到处都贴着拿你的告示
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.76,0:36:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父亲举家避难到陈留去了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.06,0:36:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是为你的安危日夜悬心哪
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.77,0:36:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父 这位是中牟县令陈公台
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.87,0:36:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}若不是他相救
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.87,0:36:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}侄儿早就粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.04,0:36:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义士大恩 要是没你
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.84,0:36:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿瞒他就活不到今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.84,0:36:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受老夫一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.55,0:36:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.65,0:36:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父高义 晚辈十分敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.75,0:36:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走走走 回家去 走走走
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.96,0:36:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.36,0:36:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.06,0:36:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧杀猪宰羊 温酒设宴
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.56,0:36:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把所有好吃的全拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.16,0:36:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.26,0:36:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我等饥寒交迫
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.47,0:36:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经两天都没有进食了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.57,0:36:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿瞒哪 这就是你家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.47,0:36:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}暂且住下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.77,0:36:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}过了风头再走也不迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.84,0:36:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕伯 家里没酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.14,0:36:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}赶紧沽酒去啊 好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.74,0:36:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到镇上 沽好酒
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:36:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.75,0:36:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.95,0:37:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在镇上到处都贴满了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.55,0:37:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搜拿我们两个人的告示
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.75,0:37:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是万一他们有的人贪图赏金
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.56,0:37:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂不是给老伯惹祸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.46,0:37:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}伯父 我等就不吃酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.86,0:37:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有碗饭充饥即可
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.96,0:37:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那哪儿成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你阿瞒是最好酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.36,0:37:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到我这儿来没有酒供你喝
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.27,0:37:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那不成
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.77,0:37:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沽酒 不叫他们去 我自己去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.17,0:37:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走走走走走
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.37,0:37:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}进屋 进屋 进屋
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.07,0:37:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到我这儿来呀没酒喝可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.24,0:37:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来来来来来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.45,0:37:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}褐二 哎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.85,0:37:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点 快去把毛驴给我牵过来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.65,0:37:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.05,0:37:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好嘞 马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.58,0:38:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.55,0:38:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快醒醒 你听 是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.85,0:38:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快快 把院门拦住
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.25,0:38:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要让那贼货跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.65,0:38:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快拿刀来 把那厮绑起来宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.85,0:38:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我去关门 你去拿刀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.66,0:38:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.67,0:39:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来他们想杀了你我二人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.57,0:39:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}提人头请官领赏
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.88,0:39:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不是说过你伯父急公好义
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.08,0:39:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你宁可不信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.48,0:39:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不会不信吕伯奢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.25,0:39:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是说过这话
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.45,0:39:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可我还说过
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.05,0:39:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人可以为了半斗粮谷卖友求荣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.15,0:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今世风日下 人心难料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.76,0:39:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说吕伯奢到镇上去沽酒
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.06,0:39:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}趁机通风报信
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.66,0:39:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}找官兵来捉拿我们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.26,0:39:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}断然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.66,0:39:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那可怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.47,0:39:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.77,0:39:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}唯有以死相拼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.77,0:39:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀出一条血路方能脱身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.57,0:39:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.48,0:39:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们准备好了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.58,0:39:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都准备好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.55,0:39:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我刀可是磨好了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.85,0:39:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}行了 行了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.85,0:39:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先进去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.85,0:39:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}进去吧 进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.65,0:39:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我门已经关上了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.95,0:39:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们可快着点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.36,0:39:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贱货 这就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.55,0:40:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀人啦 杀人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.67,0:40:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.35,0:41:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孟德
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.17,0:41:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们作孽了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.97,0:41:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}误会他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.17,0:41:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们不是要杀我们 是要杀猪
